                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370918-2154-offence-1 t18370918-cd-112"></join>8th of September</rs>, 1 pair of trowsers, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370918-name-723" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370918-name-723" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
